Package Description
application
Provides a runnable application to transform a ServiceModeller configuration file to BPMN output format.
bpmImport
Provides a parser for the ServiceModeller configuration files and classes for internal representation of their XML data,
Provides an importer for transformation of the temporal service graph structure to Business Process Model memory model.
bpmImport.smParser
Provides a parser for the ServiceModeller configuration files and classes for internal representation of their XML data.
bpmLayout
Provides an interface to produce the graphical layout of the BPM memory model and an implementation of a simple layout algorithm.
bpmnCore
Provides classes for transformation of the internal XML representation of an configuration file to a temporal service graph.
bpmnExport
Provides an interface to export the memory model to a specific output format like BPMN or XPDL.
